.7319, 1.7306, 1.7314, 1.7297, 1.7296, 1.7302, 1.7268, 1.7297, 1.7365, 1.7407, 1.7382, 1.7387, 1.7389, 1.7401, 1.7418, 1.7346, 1.7385, 1.7393, 1.7391, 1.7395, 1.7361, 1.7343, 1.7369, 1.7366, 1.7373, 1.7389, 1.7384, 1.7359, 1.7332, 1.7308, 1.729, 1.7303, 1.7301, 1.7329, 1.7249, 1.7184, 1.7157, 1.7034, 1.6971, 1.711, 1.716, 1.7149, 1.7155, 1.7146, 1.7128, 1.7158, 1.7184, 1.7164, 1.7168, 1.7183, 1.7162, 1.7219, 1.715, 1.7176, 1.7212, 1.7176, 1.7216, 1.7237, 1.7245, 1.7263, 1.7261, 1.7241, 1.7212, 1.7189, 1.7244, 1.725, 1.7262, 1.7213, 1.7186, 1.7226, 1.7283, 1.7271, 1.7266, 1.7313, 1.732, 1.7323, 1.7289, 1.7283, 1.724, 1.7227, 1.7214, 1.7243, 1.7281, 1.729, 1.7299, 1.7344, 1.7423, 1.738, 1.7353, 1.7313, 1.7337, 1.7338, 1.7351, 1.7311, 1.7346, 1.7349, 1.7399, 1.7417, 1.7429, 1.7393, 1.736, 1.7367, 1.7407, 1.7421, 1.7449, 1.7422, 1.748, 1.743, 1.7456, 1.7511, 1.7525, 1.7523, 1.75, 1.7511, 1.7516, 1.7579, 1.7624, 1.7606, 1.7557, 1.7555, 1.7556, 1.7528, 1.7554, 1.7613, 1.7627, 1.7652, 1.7659, 1.7778, 1.7785, 1.7788, 1.7848, 1.7891, 1.7939, 1.7848, 1.776, 1.7791, 1.7734, 1.7862, 1.7956, 1.8002, 1.7985, 1.8015, 1.8057, 1.8118, 1.8096, 1.8087, 1.8163, 1.8165, 1.8137, 1.8062, 1.8055, 1.8081, 1.8118, 1.8099, 1.811, 1.8107, 1.8108, 1.8166, 1.8144, 1.8112, 1.8105, 1.8146, 1.8165, 1.8189, 1.8277, 1.821, 1.8143, 1.8131, 1.8069, 1.8152, 1.8178, 1.817, 1.8205, 1.8247, 1.8288, 1.8247, 1.8228, 1.8259, 1.8356, 1.8412, 1.836, 1.8283, 1.8337, 1.8276, 1.8217, 1.8207, 1.8369, 1.8321, 1.8359, 1.8299, 1.8249, 1.8252, 1.8154, 1.8127, 1.8045, 1.8018, 1.7993], "summary_html": "<h1>期限结构因子剖析及策略优化 | Sharpe 1.32 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略基于商品期货期限结构（carry）因子构建截面多空组合。核心思想是：期货持有收益 = 现货收益 + 展期收益，而品种间展期收益与总收益的截面相关性高达 0.83，因此展期收益可以有效预测品种未来截面收益排序。</p>\n<p>最优变体使用三因子组合——去趋势展期收益（ryminusema252）、累乘展期收益（rycumprod）和平滑展期收益（ry_sm120），通过截面排名转为连续信号后加权合成，再经 IC gate 品种过滤和波动率目标缩放生成最终仓位。三因子分别捕捉短期 carry 变化、长期 carry 水平和中期 carry 趋势，组合后比单因子更稳健。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.28</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.2%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.6%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2480</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.23</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.76</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.09 / 1.38</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.52</td><td>1.93</td><td>0.49</td><td>1.16</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.24</span></td><td>1.06</td><td>1.15</td><td>1.56</td><td>1.28</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.15</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.85</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>rycumprod</code></td><td>展期收益累乘</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ifjy</code></td><td>是否交易</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 6040 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 6040 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>52</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2482</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>26.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>三因子组合信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">S_i^{combo} = w_1 \\cdot \\text{rank}_{cs}(\\text{ryminusema252}_i) + w_2 \\cdot \\text{rank}_{cs}(\\text{rycumprod}_i) + w_3 \\cdot \\text{rank}_{cs}(\\text{ry\\_sm120}_i)</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ryminusema252}_i = ry_i - \\text{EMA}_{252}(ry_i)</span>：去趋势展期收益，捕捉短期 carry 偏离</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{rycumprod}_i = \\prod_{t} (1 + ry_{i,t})</span>：累乘展期收益，反映长期 carry 水平</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ry\\_sm120}_i = \\frac{1}{120} \\sum_{k=0}^{119} ry_{i,t-k}</span>：120 日平滑展期收益</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{rank}_{cs}</span>：截面百分位排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to [-1, 1]</span> 连续信号</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">w_1=0.4, w_2=0.3, w_3=0.3</span>（最优权重组合）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>仓位缩放：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = S_i^{combo} \\cdot \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\sigma_{realized,i}^{60d}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.863)</strong>: 实现5个基础因子（ry_sm60, ry_sm140, basis, ryema252, rycumprod）和3个改进变体（Sharpe过滤+自相关方向）。rycumprod_H10表现最优(0.863)。诊断发现时序IC几乎为零(0.002)，截面IC=0.015，确认这是纯截面因子。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.910)</strong>: 在R1基础上扩展参数网格（hold={10,20,40}，smooth={60,120}），加入IC gate和归一化变体。ryema252_H20升为最优(0.910)。发现更长hold period能有效降低turnover提升Sharpe。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.216)</strong>: 关键转折 -- 引入combo因子（60% ryema252 + 40% rycumprod），将短期carry变化与长期carry水平融合。combo_6040_H30_raw实现1.216，比单因子提升33%。半样本稳定性优异（1.04/1.50），确认信号质量。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（约 50 个流动品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 30 天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面信号（非时序），品种内 TS IC 接近 0</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 依赖展期收益数据（ry 等字段），数据非空率约 37%\n<p>- 2016 年和 2021 年策略表现较弱（年度 Sharpe &lt; 0.2） - BU（沥青）、SR（白糖）、RM（菜粕）品种持续亏损 - 与因子库现有 carry 因子高度相关（corr=0.80），属于 carry 类因子的优化版本</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9836</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.49s</li>\n</ul>"}